entries.title: RTX 4090 connectors are melting again, and this time there’s a major change
entries.description: After a bit of a reprieve, we've just heard of another case of the RTX 4090 connector melting. This time, there's a major difference.

entries.title: Amazing Atlas robot shows it’s almost ready for work
entries.description: A new video released by the tech wizards at Boston Dynamics reveals how its Atlas robot could one day be usefully deployed in the workplace.
